  "time_ut": 1657190828,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dbb\u0dca\u0db6\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc4\u0dda\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc0  \u0dbb\u0da2\u0dba \u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0dc0\u0da7\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The reason for the crisis is that the government is deceiving the people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Opposition leader Mr. Sajith Premadasa said in Colombo today (7) that the current government has deceived the people in every field and due to such deception, the country is currently facing a huge crisis.",
        "The leader of the opposition mentioned that the people including himself have never deceived the people as an opposition and even from the opposition they have done a lot of work for the people under the 'Husma' program.",
        "He said this in a discussion held with various parties at the opposition leader's office that Samagi Janabalawega is a party with a social democratic program.",
        "The leader of the opposition said that the government had even deceived the farmers and that due to shortage of fertilizers, the harvest of Maas season has decreased by 50 percent.",
        "A group of party representatives, including Janasetha Peramuna party leader Battaramulale Selarathana Thera, were present for this."
      ],
